        </p>
        <h2><span class="section-emoji" aria-hidden="true">👋</span><span class="lang-en">About Me</span><span class="lang-zh">关于我</span></h2>
        <div class="lang-en">
          <p>
            Hi, I am Jiaqi Li, an undergraduate student at the
            <a href="https://www.coe.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">College of Engineering</a>,
            <a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peking University</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            My interests span mathematics, mechanics, computer science, and intelligent science.
            I have also created practice platforms for several related courses; see the
            <a href="/blog/">blog</a> in the upper-right corner for details.
          </p>
          <p>
            I am also an undergraduate student in
            <a href="http://www2.coe.pku.edu.cn/subpaget.asp?id=663" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Assoc. Prof. Mohan Chen</a>'s
            <a href="http://www2.coe.pku.edu.cn/subpaget.asp?id=664" target="_blank" rel="noopener">research group</a>
            at the <a href="https://capt.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Center for Applied Physics and Technology</a>,
            <a href="https://www.aais.pku.edu.cn/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Academy for Advanced Interdisciplinary Studies</a>,
            and the <a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Peking University</a>
            <a href="https://mech.pku.edu.cn/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">School of Mechanics and Engineering Science</a>
            <a href="https://mech.pku.edu.cn/xsdh/kxjsyzngcx1_2c2f3dbf2c5443afaf96e75cea4556f3/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Department of Scientific Computing and Engineering Intelligence</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lang-zh">
          <p>
            你好，我是李家齐，目前就读于
            <a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北京大学</a><a href="https://www.coe.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">工学院</a>。
          </p>
          <p>
            我对数学、力学、计算机科学、智能科学等多个领域颇有兴趣，也为部分课程整理了练习与复习网站，
            可通过右上角的<a href="/blog/">动态</a>查看。
          </p>
          <p>
            我也是
            <a href="http://www2.coe.pku.edu.cn/subpaget.asp?id=663" target="_blank" rel="noopener">陈默涵老师</a>
            <a href="http://www2.coe.pku.edu.cn/subpaget.asp?id=664" target="_blank" rel="noopener">课题组</a>
            的本科生；该课题组所在单位包括
            <a href="https://capt.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北京大学应用物理与技术研究中心</a>、
            <a href="https://www.aais.pku.edu.cn/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北京大学前沿交叉学科研究院</a>，以及
            <a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">北京大学</a><a href="https://mech.pku.edu.cn/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">力学与工程科学学院</a><a href="https://mech.pku.edu.cn/xsdh/kxjsyzngcx1_2c2f3dbf2c5443afaf96e75cea4556f3/index.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">科学计算与工程智能系</a>。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="interests" class="academic-section">
        <h2><span class="section-emoji" aria-hidden="true">🔬</span><span class="lang-en">Research Interests</span><span class="lang-zh">研究兴趣</span></h2>
        <ul class="plain-list lang-en">
          <li>Mathematics for computing: linear algebra, probability, optimization, and symbolic reasoning.</li>
          <li>Systems and parallel programming: MPI, OpenMP, CUDA, and performance-oriented implementation.</li>
          <li>Readable learning infrastructure: notes, review materials, and small tools for self-study.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="plain-list lang-zh">
          <li>面向计算的数学：线性代数、概率、优化与符号推理。</li>
          <li>系统与并行程序设计：MPI、OpenMP、CUDA 与面向性能的实现。</li>
          <li>可读的学习基础设施：笔记、复习资料与自学小工具。</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

